data.name: rtbHowToPlay.Text
data.value:
Velocity.x is a fast paced game where players will try to achieve high speeds by anwering random Fraction problems.
Controls: Users must press start to beging the game, random questions will pop up and users must answer these correctly
If answer is correct: the speed will increase.
If answer is incorrect: the game will end.
Watch out for bonus questions that are challenging, but help you gain even more speed!
